---
title: Cheesy French Bean & Onion Dip with Garlic & Thyme | Serves 2
description: Dive into cheesy, gooey goodness with this French-inspired dip! Packed with hearty cannellini beans, caramelised onions, and Parmesan cheese, this dip is a flavour-packed party in every bite. Perfect with crackers, veggies, or just a spoon (we won’t judge), it’s your new go-to for snacking or entertaining!
